            <p>Whether you are traveling for business or leisure, <b>Paris Charles de Gaulle Airport</b> can provide the services necessary to make your stay both efficient and comfortable. Designed to offer a boutique workspace for passengers on the go to work, unwind, and prepare for their next port of call. </p>

